title: Adams Memorial Commission | The Adams Memorial Commission
description: The Adams Memorial Commission (AMC) is a congressional commission created to establishing a memorial for John Adams, Abigail Adams, John Quincy Adams, Louisa Catherine Adams, Henry Adams, Charles Adams and the Adams Family.
